html(lang='en')
  head
    title QR Code Generator With Text for URLs, websites, events, etc.
    script(src='//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.9.0.min.js')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/twitter-bootstrap/2.2.2/css/bootstrap-combined.min.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootswatch/2.1.1/readable/bootstrap.min.css')
    script(src='//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/twitter-bootstrap/2.2.2/js/bootstrap.min.js')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/main.css')
    script(src='client.js')

  body
    h1 Get your awesome QR code.
    div(id='content')
      div(class='textbox-div')
        | URL/text to encode: 
        input(type='text', id='string-text', placeholder="My site, e.g. http://jezzpaul.com", autofocus)
      div(class='textbox-div')
        | Text to overlay: 
        input(type='text', id='qr-text', placeholder="My initials, e.g. PHB")
      div(id='button-div')
        button(type='button', id='go-button', class='btn btn-primary', data-loading-text='Loading...', onclick='goTime();') QR Go Time
    div#mycred
      | A site by 
      a(href='mailto:thepaulbooth@gmail.com', id='name-link') Paul Booth 
      |  : 
      a(href='http://twitter.com/thepaulbooth', id='twitter-link') @thepaulbooth